<div class="row about-container">
   <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-6 col-lg-6 col-xl-6 about-text-container">
      <div id="about-heading"><h2>Who are we?</h2><hr></div>
      <p>We are a team that wanted to make something different. An idea of being able to request services and get them done without having to pay money. What will happen instead is in exchange for a person helping you. You will exhange a service back as payment instead of using money. This will give everyone a chance to get services done like someone help mow the lawn or someone help changing your oil without having to pay money. If you have a certain skill the other party is looking for. You are then able to message each other through the app and come to a mutual agreement of exchange.</p>
    </div>
