    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-6 col-lg-6 col-xl-6 offer-image-container">
      <img src="../img/working.jpg">
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-6 col-lg-6 col-xl-6 offer-text-container">
      <div id="offer-heading"><h2>What do we offer?</h2><hr></div>
      <p>This app offers an exchange of services like helping someone fix the fence or helping change a tire without having to pay money for that service. We are a mutual aid service where you can request a service and someone can look through by the city and find your request. The other party can then message you through the app and both of you can come to a mutual agreement on the exhance of services that will happen. You can tell them the skills that you offer like if you are a graphic designer and you can make flyers and logos then you have that to offer to the other party.</p>
      <a href="">Sign up today</a>
